title: Episode 129: Lip Service Live - The Valentine’s Day Special (ft Amara La Negra)
itunes:title: Episode 129: Lip Service Live - The Valentine’s Day Special (ft Amara La Negra)
description:
For this weeks episode, the ladies of Lip Service host their second ever Live Show in NYC! During this special Valentine’s Day edition, Amara La Negra from Love and Hip Hop Miami opens up about her sex life, past relationships, and her weaknesses in men!
